name: Tuscan Kale Salad
description: A fresh Tuscan Kale Salad served with crisp Hudson Valley apples, toasted pumpkin seeds, crumbled goat cheese, and drizzled with balsamic vinaigrette.

name: Romaine Caesar Salad
description: A fresh Caesar salad made with crispy romaine lettuce, cherry tomatoes, roasted garlic, and a Parmesan crisp on top.

name: Cobb Wedge Salad
description: A hearty Cobb Wedge Salad with iceberg lettuce, smoked chicken, avocado, crispy bacon, blue cheese, a hard-boiled egg, and ranch dressing.

name: Mac N Cheese Lollipops
description: Crispy Mac N Cheese Lollipops made with a four-cheese blend and coated in panko breadcrumbs, served with a dipping sauce.

name: Warm Artichoke & Kale Dip
description: A creamy artichoke and kale dip served with crispy corn tortilla chips, perfect for dipping.

name: All Natural Beef Blend Burger
description: A juicy beef burger with crispy applewood smoked bacon, served on a soft bun with lettuce, tomato, and a side of fries.

name: Ahi Tuna Burger
description: A seared ahi tuna burger topped with sriracha tartar sauce, served on a toasted bun with fresh greens and a side of fries.
